data.description: Beautiful move in ready home located in the Centennial Hills area, close to shopping, parks, and easy freeway access. Home features an open floor plan, with bamboo wood flooring in the family room. Kitchen has granite countertops, island, and bar area. Great size backyard with grass area, patio, & planter area. 4 bedrooms. Large master bedroom & bathroom with two sinks, tub and shower. Community features a large gated pool with a covered gazebo!
